title: B-Town celebs wish Happy Dussehra to fans
text: Amitabh Bachchan Celebrates 73rd Birthday | Meets Fans & Press Conference PART 2 17:02 Megastar Amitabh Bachchan turned 73 on Sunday 11th October, 2015. He celebrated his birthday with the members of the media and also met his fans who gathered outside his Mumbai home, Jalsa to wish him a very Happy Birthday. Watch Amitabh addressing the Press on his birthday in this video.
